    <dd><p>Group name field, length 1~60, beginning with a letter or underscore, can contain alphanumeric underscore.</p>

## Import



tsf group can be imported using the id, e.g.

```sh
 $ pulumi import tencentcloud:Tsf/group:Group group group-axxx
```
